  |   "d"  |                | 		    |              | 
  |--------|----------------|---------------|--------------|
  |        |                |               |              |
  |nbound=3| Omega_cc^+(s)  | Omega_bc^0(s) | Omega_bb^-(s)|
  |   "s"  |                |               |              |
